overview.en: YT [YibiToken] (hereinafter referred to as YT) is the passport of Yibi ecology, a P2P electronic cryptocurrency developed based on ETH2.0, and the representative of all the rights and interests of Yibi ecology itself.
overview.zh: YT【YibiToken】（以下简称YT）是一币生态的通行证，是基于以太坊2.0开发出来的一种P2P的电子密码货币，是一币生态自身所有权益的代表。
